ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: You will learn so much! An incredibly valuable course, and great seminar discussions.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I wrote my senior thesis under this class and it really allowed me to find the nuances of a subject that I knew much about, but not necessarily too critically. I appreciated that Professor Smith understood the "rage against the machine" mentality but still pushed me to find the intellectual pieces that brought my thesis to the next level. He was incredibly helpful in office hours and the class material greatly aided my research, but he allowed my ideas to take shape without constraining them to the course. It was a fantastic class and I am grateful to have had the opportunity to write my thesis with it.
